cascading.tap.local
Class FileTap

java.lang.Object
  cascading.tap.Tap<Properties,InputStream,OutputStream>
      cascading.tap.local.FileTap
All Implemented Interfaces:
cascading.flow.FlowElement, cascading.tap.type.FileType<Properties>, Serializable
public class FileTap
extends cascading.tap.Tap<Properties,InputStream,OutputStream>
implements cascading.tap.type.FileType<Properties>

Class FileTap is a Tap sub-class that allows for direct local file access.

FileTap must be used with the LocalFlowConnector to create Flow instances that run in "local" mode.
